title: Consensus Check: Raise the proposal quorum threshold
body:
Raise the proposal quorum threshold from 40M because recent voting participation is much higher and there is a lot of UNI that has been delegated.

Please vote for what you think the new quorum threshold should be set to.
author: 0x070341aA5Ed571f0FB2c4a5641409B1A46b4961b
